# Plan Status Sync

Keep `PLAN.local.md` and `docs/SUPPORTED.md` in sync with actual project state.

## When completing a work package

1. Mark WP done in `PLAN.local.md` Session Bootstrap Snapshot
2. Update `docs/SUPPORTED.md` if the WP adds platform support
3. If WP adds a package, verify its README exists and is linked

## When starting a new WP

- Confirm dependencies are marked done in `PLAN.local.md`
- Read the WP brief in `.github/internal/wp/WPn.md`

## Breaking changes

Use Changesets (`.changeset/`) for all breaking changes:
- Include migration example in changeset description
- For v0.x: breaking changes expected, document clearly
- For v1.0+: follow semver strictly
